{"tid":610692,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"分享下一款好少茶樓有既點心","createTime":"2018-03-30T07:43:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T11:26:23.000Z","uid":62277,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ea70266677817486059dcdd0fe34795d45bd863","tid":610692,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T07:43:07.000Z","msg":"最近收到觀音娘娘命令<br />\n要揾曬全港既蛋黃千層糕出黎<br />\n質素ok而價錢亦較為貼地既廣東茶居已執笠<br />\n真係選擇無多<br />\n<br />\n呢間唔算做得出色<br />\n但係過下囗癮都可以接受既<br />\n至少比元朗老馮好<br />\n落鹹蛋黃份量唔少<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/153738_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F153738_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3b3f4736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n出面有好多茶樓點心紙上<br />\n都有千層馬拉糕/奶黄千層糕<br />\n其實同蛋黃千層糕係兩回事黎<br />\n<br />\n奶黃千層糕<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/30/154151_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F30%2F154151_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=11e6c408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叫蛋黃千層糕/古法千層糕既先係正貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b950980c6a37bc82564eb30b796ff6defe68aa59","tid":610692,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"雞包仔，四寶雞扎（齊四寶）"},{"pid":"e74fd356a4afd2fc0d8d0cd157c20effea286514","tid":610692,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:16:07.000Z","msg":"sor冇睇清楚內文，原來唔係一人分享n樣"},{"pid":"6df0cf566c78f977f96fadf11bc61a7b0ec6986e","tid":610692,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b950980c6a37bc82564eb30b796ff6defe68aa59","tid":610692,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T08:14:50.000Z","msg":"雞包仔，四寶雞扎（齊四寶）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2